title: Inbound visitor growth in the Middle East 2011 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Year-over-year visitor growth, containing a total of 9 data points.
In general Year-over-year visitor growth has rose over the Year.

Year-over-year visitor growth is roughly constant from 2011 to 2013, slightly increasing from 2013 to 2014, slightly decreasing from 2014 to 2015, slightly increasing from 2015 to 2017, and lastly roughly constant from 2017 to 2019.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Year-over-year visitor growth, about 8.0 was reported at Year 2014
The lowest Year-over-year visitor growth, of value 1.2 was reported at Year 2016
